TopicTitle: Where have you not been in KSP yet!

Articles.Content:
Hands down, where have you not been in KSP so far?

I made a list which I'm going to work through.

I've never been to (landed on)

- Gilly

- Ike

- Dres

- Laythe

- Bob

- Pol

- Eeloo

 

Why? I dunno, I was just shocked when I realized how long the list still is. 

Edited May 7, 2017 by Physics Student

I've been to Moho, just not landed on it. I've also been to Eeloo but it was in OPM so I don't think that counts.

Edit: I've also never landed on Laythe but forgot to vote on it.

Edited May 7, 2017 by The Raging Sandwich
I have a lander/orbiter combo in jool orbit. I plan to land it on laythe soon.
I've been to everywhere, except Bop. Hmmmmmmmmmmm that is suspicious..
I've landed everywhere on that list, although I may not have landed crew everywhere since 1.0. I've never been to the bottom of any ocean...

I haven't done a return trip from Eve, though had a capable craft.

And possibly not from Gilly either. It was my 1st interplanetary flight way back in v0.22, so i can't remember how it ended.
Eeloo and Moho. Made a massive ship with space plane and Landers that I smashed Dres and Jool system with.
I've landed on every body except the Sun, but I've never returned from Eve or Jool's surface.
I have only landed on the Moon.
